de.ailis.usb4java.libusb

Class EndpointDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ailis.usb4java.libusb.EndpointDescriptor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.usb.UsbDescriptor, javax.usb.UsbEndpointDescriptor

    public final class EndpointDescriptor
extends Object
implements javax.usb.UsbEndpointDescriptor
    A structure representing the standard USB endpoint descriptor. This descriptor is documented in section 9.6.6 of the USB 3.0 specification. All multiple-byte fields are represented in host-endian format.
    Author:
    Klaus Reimer (k@ailis.de)
